<lb n="0783a09" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0783a10" ed="T"/><head type="no">No. 1817 [cf. Nos. 1510, 1514]</head>
<lb n="0783a11" ed="T"/><juan n="001" fun="open"><mulu n="1" type="卷"/><jhead><note n="0783001" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">【原】麗本</note>略明般若末後一頌讚述</jhead></juan>
<lb n="0783a12" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0783a13" ed="T"/><byline type="Author"><note n="0783002" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">述號新加</note>唐三藏法師義淨述</byline>
<lb n="0783a14" ed="T"/><div1 type="jing"><p id="pT40p0783a1401">義淨因譯無著菩薩般若頌釋訖。詳夫大士
<lb n="0783a15" ed="T"/>判其九喻。可謂文致幽深。理義玄簡。自非地
<lb n="0783a16" ed="T"/>&CB00444;極喜。誰能發此明慧。而西域相承云。無著
<lb n="0783a17" ed="T"/>菩薩昔於&CB00418;史多天慈氏尊處。親受此八十
<lb n="0783a18" ed="T"/>頌。開般若要門。順瑜伽宗理。明唯識之義。遂
<lb n="0783a19" ed="T"/>令教流印度。若金烏之焰赫扶桑。義闡神州。
<lb n="0783a20" ed="T"/>等玉兔之光浮雪嶺。然而能斷金剛。西方乃
<lb n="0783a21" ed="T"/>有多釋。考其始也此頌最先。即世親大士躬
<lb n="0783a22" ed="T"/>為其釋此。雖神州譯訖。而義有闕如。故復親
<lb n="0783a23" ed="T"/>覈談筵。重詳其妙。雅符釋意。更譯本經。世親
<lb n="0783a24" ed="T"/>菩薩復為般若七門義釋。而那爛陀寺盛傳
<lb n="0783a25" ed="T"/>其論。但為義府幽&CB00287;尋者莫測。有師子月法
<lb n="0783a26" ed="T"/>師造此論釋。復有東印度多聞俗士其名月
<lb n="0783a27" ed="T"/>官。遍檢諸家亦為義釋。斯等莫不意符三性。
<lb n="0783a28" ed="T"/>不同中觀矣。更有別釋。而但順龍猛。不會瑜
<lb n="0783a29" ed="T"/>伽。瑜伽則真有俗無。以三性為本。中觀乃真
<pb n="0783b" id="T40.1817.0783b" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0783b01" ed="T"/>無俗有。<note n="0783003" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">寔＝實【三】【宮】＊</note><note n="0783003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">寔＝實【宋】【元】【明】【宮】＊</note><app n="0783003"><lem wit="【大】">寔</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">實</rdg></app>二諦為先。般若大宗。含斯<note n="0783004" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">兩＝雨【宋】</note><app n="0783004"><lem wit="【大】">兩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">雨</rdg></app>意。
<lb n="0783b02" ed="T"/>致使東夏則道分南北。西方乃義隔有空。既
<lb n="0783b03" ed="T"/>識<note n="0783005" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">介＝分【三】【宮】</note><note n="0783005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">介＝分【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0783005"><lem wit="【大】">介</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">分</rdg></app>綱。理無和雜。各准　聖旨誠難乖競。
<lb n="0783b04" ed="T"/>然而末後一頌云。一切有為法如星<note n="0783006" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB00622;＝翳【三】【宮】下同</note><note n="0783006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">&CB00622;＝翳【宋】【元】【明】【宮】下同</note><app n="0783006"><lem wit="【大】">&CB00622;</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">翳</rdg></app>燈幻。
<lb n="0783b05" ed="T"/>露泡夢電雲。應作如是觀者。而釋文既隱。恐
<lb n="0783b06" ed="T"/>尋者尚昧。輒因二九事喻。聊題十八之作。冀
<lb n="0783b07" ed="T"/>使朝覽遂閑。庶罔銷神之滯。夜光親授。長無
<lb n="0783b08" ed="T"/>按劍之惑。然而見等九<note n="0783007" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">事＝等【三】【宮】</note><note n="0783007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">事＝等【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0783007"><lem wit="【大】">事</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">等</rdg></app>。即生死之區寰。
<lb n="0783b09" ed="T"/>大士了如星等。是故處而不著。智不住生津。
<lb n="0783b10" ed="T"/>&CB00104;紅蓮之在瀲。悲不居圓寂。若白玉之沈溺。
<lb n="0783b11" ed="T"/>因答無住涅槃。<note n="0783008" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">申＝中【三】【宮】</note><note n="0783008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">申＝中【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0783008"><lem wit="【大】">申</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">中</rdg></app>其九喻云爾。</p>
<lb n="0783b12" ed="T"/><p id="pT40p0783b1201">論見　觀見如星長夜妄執。</p>
<lb n="0783b13" ed="T"/><lg id="lgT40p0783b1301"><l>見心長夜景</l><l>妄執久冥舒</l>
<lb n="0783b14" ed="T"/><l>三心纔已發</l><l>兩分盡皆除</l></lg>
<lb n="0783b15" ed="T"/><p id="pT40p0783b1501">喻星　以星喻見夜有明無。</p>
<lb n="0783b16" ed="T"/><lg id="lgT40p0783b1601"><l>榆星通夜景</l><l>柳色徹明舒</l>
<lb n="0783b17" ed="T"/><l>千條光若發</l><l>一旦盡皆除</l></lg>
<lb n="0783b18" ed="T"/><p id="pT40p0783b1801">論境　道境如&CB00622;妄&CB00418;空花。</p>
<lb n="0783b19" ed="T"/><lg id="lgT40p0783b1901"><l>境色無非障</l><l>妄有見塵瑕</l>
<lb n="0783b20" ed="T"/><l>但由真智力</l><l>不復&CB00418;狂花</l></lg>
<lb n="0783b21" ed="T"/><p id="pT40p0783b2101">喻&CB00622;　以&CB00622;喻境元無妄執。</p>
<lb n="0783b22" ed="T"/><lg id="lgT40p0783b2201"><l>太虛本無障</l><l>淨境性<note n="0783009" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">亡＝忘【三】【宮】</note><note n="0783009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">亡＝忘【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0783009"><lem wit="【大】">亡</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">忘</rdg></app>瑕</l>
<lb n="0783b23" ed="T"/><l>但由&CB00622;眼力</l><l>遂使見空花</l></lg>
<lb n="0783b24" ed="T"/><p id="pT40p0783b2401">論識　言識如燈生生不絕。</p>
<lb n="0783b25" ed="T"/><lg id="lgT40p0783b2501"><l>見起起不已</l><l>妄生生未極</l>
<lb n="0783b26" ed="T"/><l>留滯死宮中</l><l>良由依識力</l></lg>
<lb n="0783b27" ed="T"/><p id="pT40p0783b2701">喻燈　以燈喻識焰焰無窮。</p>
<lb n="0783b28" ed="T"/><lg id="lgT40p0783b2801"><l>發焰焰不已</l><l>舒光光未極</l>
<lb n="0783b29" ed="T"/><l>照灼炳<note n="0783010" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">宵＝霄【三】【宮】</note><note n="0783010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">宵＝霄【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0783010"><lem wit="【大】">宵</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">霄</rdg></app>中</l><l>良<note n="0783011" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">為＝由【三】【宮】</note><note n="0783011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">為＝由【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0783011"><lem wit="【大】">為</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">由</rdg></app>膏油力</l></lg>
<pb n="0783c" id="T40.1817.0783c" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0783c01" ed="T"/><p id="pT40p0783c0101">論界　說界如幻藉業生而會盡。</p>
<lb n="0783c02" ed="T"/><lg id="lgT40p0783c0201"><l>業功莊處巧</l><l>由惑生眾相</l>
<lb n="0783c03" ed="T"/><l><note n="0783012" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">所＝妄【三】</note><note n="0783012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">所＝妄【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0783012"><lem wit="【大】">所</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">妄</rdg></app>執定非真</l><l>界體<note n="0783013" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">全＝令【宮】</note><app n="0783013"><lem wit="【大】">全</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">令</rdg></app>虛妄</l></lg>
<lb n="0783c04" ed="T"/><p id="pT40p0783c0401">喻幻　以幻喻界假匠起而終無。</p>
<lb n="0783c05" ed="T"/><lg id="lgT40p0783c0501"><l>幻師方便巧</l><l>假作眾形相</l>
<lb n="0783c06" ed="T"/><l>鞠體固非真</l><l>所見皆虛妄</l></lg>
<lb n="0783c07" ed="T"/><p id="pT40p0783c0701">論身　序身如露體不久停。</p>
<lb n="0783c08" ed="T"/><lg id="lgT40p0783c0801"><l>投軀生巘<note n="0783014" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">際＝隔【宋】【元】【宮】</note><app n="0783014"><lem wit="【大】">際</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【宮】">隔</rdg></app></l><l>寄命死河中</l>
<lb n="0783c09" ed="T"/><l>鎮處飄颻夜</l><l>還如橐籥風</l></lg>
<lb n="0783c10" ed="T"/><p id="pT40p0783c1001">喻露　以露喻身逢風必落。</p>
<lb n="0783c11" ed="T"/><lg id="lgT40p0783c1101"><l>圓珠停草際</l><l><note n="0783015" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">渧＝滴【明】＊</note><app n="0783015"><lem wit="【大】">渧</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">滴</rdg></app>淚處華中</l>
<lb n="0783c12" ed="T"/><l>悽悽動林夜</l><l>索索盡隨風</l></lg>
<lb n="0783c13" ed="T"/><p id="pT40p0783c1301">論受用　陳用如泡待根境識。</p>
<lb n="0783c14" ed="T"/><lg id="lgT40p0783c1401"><l>寰中根色積</l><l>託此<note n="0783016" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">復＝腹【明】</note><app n="0783016"><lem wit="【大】">復</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">腹</rdg></app>心行</l>
<lb n="0783c15" ed="T"/><l><app source="0783003" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">寔</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">實</rdg></app>由三觸合</l><l>遂令三受生</l></lg>
<lb n="0783c16" ed="T"/><p id="pT40p0783c1601">喻泡　以泡喻用假<app source="0783015" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">渧</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">滴</rdg></app>水風。</p>
<lb n="0783c17" ed="T"/><lg id="lgT40p0783c1701"><l>池中平水積</l><l><app source="0783015" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">渧</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">滴</rdg></app>墜有風行</l>
<lb n="0783c18" ed="T"/><l>但由三事合</l><l>乘使萬泡生</l></lg>
<lb n="0783c19" ed="T"/><p id="pT40p0783c1901">論過　述過如夢由思而起。</p>
<lb n="0783c20" ed="T"/><lg id="lgT40p0783c2001"><l>過去雖無境</l><l>尋思意尚通</l>
<lb n="0783c21" ed="T"/><l>遂令方寸內</l><l>還見九城容</l></lg>
<lb n="0783c22" ed="T"/><p id="pT40p0783c2201">喻夢　以夢喻過因憶乃生。</p>
<lb n="0783c23" ed="T"/><lg id="lgT40p0783c2301"><l>處晝多緣境</l><l>良宵記念通</l>
<lb n="0783c24" ed="T"/><l>遂令於睡內</l><l>重憶本時容</l></lg>
<lb n="0783c25" ed="T"/><p id="pT40p0783c2501">論現　談現如電暫時而有。</p>
<lb n="0783c26" ed="T"/><lg id="lgT40p0783c2601"><l>萬像如電<note n="0783017" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">野＝舒【三】【宮】</note><note n="0783017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">野＝舒【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0783017"><lem wit="【大】">野</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">舒</rdg></app></l><l>四相等流光</l>
<lb n="0783c27" ed="T"/><l>詎知唯一念</l><l>妄計有三常</l></lg>
<lb n="0783c28" ed="T"/><p id="pT40p0783c2801">喻電　以電喻現&CB04918;忽便亡。</p>
<lb n="0783c29" ed="T"/><lg id="lgT40p0783c2901"><l>震雷鳴四野</l><l>擊電動<note n="0783018" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">千＝十【元】</note><app n="0783018"><lem wit="【大】">千</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】">十</rdg></app>光</l>
<pb n="0784a" id="T40.1817.0784a" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0784a01" ed="T"/><l>剎那<note n="0784001" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">存＝有【元】</note><app n="0784001"><lem wit="【大】">存</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】">有</rdg></app>有念</l><l>即體自無常</l></lg>
<lb n="0784a02" ed="T"/><p id="pT40p0784a0201">論<note n="0784002" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">未＝末【三】【宮】＊</note><note n="0784002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">未＝末【宋】【元】【明】【宮】＊</note><app n="0784002"><lem wit="【大】">未</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">末</rdg></app>　論<app source="0784002" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">未</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">末</rdg></app>如雲本識能持其種。</p>
<lb n="0784a03" ed="T"/><lg id="lgT40p0784a0301"><l>藏識無初結</l><l>波情浪後飛</l>
<lb n="0784a04" ed="T"/><l>良由有貪愛</l><l>帶種定何疑</l></lg>
<lb n="0784a05" ed="T"/><p id="pT40p0784a0501">喻雲　以雲喻<app source="0784002" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">未</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">末</rdg></app>自體必含於潤。</p>
<lb n="0784a06" ed="T"/><lg id="lgT40p0784a0601"><l>靉靆屯雲結</l><l>煥爛景風飛</l>
<lb n="0784a07" ed="T"/><l>光華如可愛</l><l>含潤理無疑</l></lg>
<lb n="0784a08" ed="T"/><p id="pT40p0784a0801">更以一句收事收喻撮其要義而為一述。</p>
<lb n="0784a09" ed="T"/><lg id="lgT40p0784a0901"><l>見心智滅如星殄</l><l>惑境真亡若&CB00622;除</l>
<lb n="0784a10" ed="T"/><l>想起由識如燈焰</l><l>界有藉思同幻車</l>
<lb n="0784a11" ed="T"/><l>一身暫顯同朝露</l><l>三受忽現等泡虛</l>
<lb n="0784a12" ed="T"/><l>憶念過時空夢發</l><l>計執現存奔電舒</l>
<lb n="0784a13" ed="T"/><l>既知雨潤雲中住</l><l><app source="0784002" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">未</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">末</rdg></app>種常依識藏居</l></lg>
<lb n="0784a14" ed="T"/><p id="pT40p0784a1401">次下別據三性三身真俗般若。以明觀<note n="0784003" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">行＋（在）【宮】</note><app n="0784003"><lem wit="【大】">行</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">行在</rdg></app>九
<lb n="0784a15" ed="T"/>喻解<note n="0784004" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">九＋（九）【明】</note><app n="0784004"><lem wit="【大】">九</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">九九</rdg></app>事云。</p>
<lb n="0784a16" ed="T"/><lg id="lgT40p0784a1601"><l>熟觀生界咸如此</l><l>智者應可務真常</l>
<lb n="0784a17" ed="T"/><l>真常實不玄</l><l>圓成在目前</l>
<lb n="0784a18" ed="T"/><l>覺二體空蛇<note n="0784005" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">索盡＝盡索【元】</note><app n="0784005"><lem wit="【大】">索盡</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】">盡索</rdg></app></l><l>了一非無鏡月懸</l>
<lb n="0784a19" ed="T"/><l>鏡月懸時實無慮</l><l>但作他緣生福處</l>
<lb n="0784a20" ed="T"/><l>唯識初心<note n="0784006" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">乍＝作【明】</note><app n="0784006"><lem wit="【大】">乍</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">作</rdg></app>有依</l><l>真如後念還無據</l>
<lb n="0784a21" ed="T"/><l>無據即般若</l><l>勝俗亡真假</l>
<lb n="0784a22" ed="T"/><l>福津如筏捐不捐</l><l>悲智隨生捨不捨</l></lg>
<lb n="0784a23" ed="T"/><juan n="001" fun="close"><jhead>略明般若末後一頌讚述</jhead></juan></div1>
